Package nl.naturalis.nda.elasticsearch.load.brahms

Package that handles the import of the Brahms data sources.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BrahmsBackupExtensionRemover
    Removes the .imported extension from CSV files that have been successfully processed, so they will be picked up again by the Brahms import programs.
    BrahmsDumpUtil Deprecated
    UTF-8 conversion now happends on the fly
    BrahmsFindInSource
    Utility class for finding values in Brahms export files.
    BrahmsImportAll
    Manages the import of Brahms specimens and multimedia.
    BrahmsImportUtil
    Provides common functionality related to the Brahms ETL cycle.
    BrahmsMultiMediaImporter
    Manages the import of Brahms multimedia.
    BrahmsMultiMediaLoader
    The loader component in the ETL cycle for Brahms multimedia.
    BrahmsMultiMediaTransformer
    The transformer component in the ETL cycle for Brahms multimedia.
    BrahmsSpecimenImporter
    Manages the import of Brahms specimens.
    BrahmsSpecimenLoader
    The loader component in the ETL cycle for Brahms specimens.
    BrahmsSpecimenTransformer
    The transformer component in the Brahms ETL cycle for specimens.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BrahmsCsvField
    Enumerates the CSV fields in a Brahms export file.
